actor User
boundary ProductPage
control ProductController
participant ":ProductService" as ProductService
participant ":ProductModel" as ProductModel
database Database


User->ProductPage: 1. Choose sort option
activate ProductPage
activate User

ProductPage->ProductController: 2. GET /products?sort=&page=&size=
activate ProductController

ProductController->ProductService: 3. Process product sorting
activate ProductService

ProductService->ProductModel: 4. Build sort criteria
activate ProductModel

ProductModel->Database: 5. Retrieve products ordered by criteria
activate Database
Database-->ProductModel: 6. Result set
deactivate Database

ProductModel-->ProductService: 7. Return sorted list + paging info
deactivate ProductModel

alt No products available
    ProductService-->ProductController: 8.1. Return empty result
    ProductController-->ProductPage: 8.1.1. Return 200 OK + empty list/message
    ProductPage-->User: 8.1.2. Show "No products available"
else Products available
    ProductService-->ProductController: 8.2. Return SortProductResponse
    deactivate ProductService
    ProductController-->ProductPage: 8.2.1. Return 200 OK + sorted products data
    deactivate ProductController


ProductPage-->User: 9. Display sorted result
end
deactivate ProductPage
deactivate User
```